                     <interp inst="t18190217-158-off916" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190217-158-cd917" type="crimeDate">9th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-158-off916 t18190217-158-cd917"></join>, one sheet, value 7 s.; one pair of trowsers, value 5 s., and one head-cloth, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190217-158-victim1349" type="victimName">
